install_msg: Thank you for installing this repository! If you encounter any issues or have any questions, feel free to reach out.
name: EmbedTracker
short: A repository of cogs for tracking Rumble Royale winners.
description: This repository contains a collection of cogs designed for tracking Rumble Royale winners, sending congratulatory messages, and handling payment confirmations. The cogs are tailored for Discord bots using the Red-DiscordBot framework.
